NAME                         REQUIRED    DEFAULT        VALUES/INFO
NODE_ENV                     yes         -              "production", "development", "test"
MONGO_URL                    yes         -              Mongoose compatible URL to mongoDB database
REDIS_URL                    yes         -              IORedis compatible URL to redis database
AUTH_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET     yes         -              Secret for JWT accesstokens
AUTH_REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET    yes         -              Secret for JWT refresshtokens
APP_PORT                     yes         "3000"         Numbers as strings from 0-65536
DEBUG                        no          "0"            "0" (debug disabled), "1" (debug mode enabled)
APP_CORS                     no          "*"            Cors origin string
AUTH_VALIDATE_EMAIL          no          "1"            "0" (email validation disabled), "1" (email validation enabled)
AUTH_EXPIRES_IN              no          "900"          Number of seconds an accesstokens is validation
AUTH_PASSWORD_RULE           no          "Y-Y-Y-Y-8"    Password rule (more on that on authfunctions/express)